WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.070
I had the chance to play with the older versions for iPhone

00:00:30.070 --> 00:00:33.230
and well, I can assure you that this new version is

00:00:33.190 --> 00:00:37.400
a lot more impressive and a lot more realistic than the previous ones.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:48.000
It's amazing how Gameloft can imitate our movements in 
 the field in such a realistic way.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:01:00.040
Yes, certainly. Almost everyone. Almost all of us, I think. There 
 are some who like them more than others, but...

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:07.000
there is no doubt that, during the trips or in hotels, we 
 have a lot of free time, a lot of pre-match

00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:15.600
preparation with long hours. And playing video games is one 
 of the ways we use to pass the time.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:26.000
It's good. You have to get used to it. It's not 
 the same as when you play with a controller, but...

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:30.050
it's very well done, it's real, and...

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.000
I recommend the video game.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:45.000
Well, to continue winning. With the National Team, we've 
 won the 2 most important championships. 

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:49.000
But we can win more, right? It's true. 

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:54.000
Winning one World Cup isn't the same as 
 winning two. Same for the European Championship.

